node.description: This library provides expression trees for representation of geometric expressions and automatic differentiation of these expressions. This enables to write down geometric expressions at the position level, and automatically compute Jacobians and higher order derivatives efficiently and without loss of precision. The library is built upon the KDL library and uses the same geometric primitives.
